Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快准备遮起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.53,0:00:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顾人怨的来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.70,0:00:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯，这次你又干了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.18,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.25,0:00:50.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.92,0:00:58.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.19,0:01:05.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.20,0:01:09.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.81,0:01:19.11,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.72,0:01:34.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.16,0:01:41.37,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.44,0:01:48.47,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.54,0:01:59.42,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}起手有回真小人\NTakeback
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么心事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只惨遭基尔特公会袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.86,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士又说要留在银之战舰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心发生红视现象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我以前也曾经碰到过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.77,0:03:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在失去知觉之前\N那感觉好难形容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我一杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时价？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.42,0:03:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这顶级水是取自即使在这里\N也很难入手的水源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天只要80克劳地亚而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80克劳地亚！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次你们又大干了一场是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是这次需要补充的弹药\N以及补给品的清单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请优先更换升降机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶着要出发\N装甲和炮台的修理也请尽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.05,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就万事拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是顶级水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会在这种地方再碰到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问…你是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？你不记得了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.19,0:04:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的水壶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…什么来着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝，莫蓝．谢兰度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…换句话说你是被炒鱿鱼了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，是我主动辞职的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是因为我们的关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你们没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外头不是停着一艘\N叫做格拉艾斯号的贵族舰吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很气派的那艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去那艘船上工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也有推荐信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要有这些生还章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是稳操胜算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳操什么胜算啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跑了 在跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这儿来怎么可以不玩这个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，借过一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来，这儿贵族还真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外头停着那艘号称\N毫发无伤的帝王格拉艾斯号喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说落跑王格拉艾斯号吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘，你说得太大声了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，可不可以让个位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天这里已经被我们包下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们周围\N你们不觉得你们身分不对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌博和阶级哪有什么相关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个佣兵还想怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道格拉艾斯号\N是直属于皇帝陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还敢这样撒野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛温
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么冲动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.74,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才刚到而已\N总之先去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝完了再赌一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.75,0:06:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等玩够了再来扯这个也不迟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爷，来一杯那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，马上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.94,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想到那种人的船上去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.54,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作轻松钱又多，不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且最棒的一点是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在格拉艾斯号上\N就绝对死不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好差哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.17,0:07:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以下去到船坞散散心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，我们一起去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我想去睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶，赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我们的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天运气不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，没闹事果然是正确的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确，正确，太正确了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的比赛\N由于跑道上有障碍物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣告无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,障碍物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庄家就和基尔特公会一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说的话就是规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想参加赌局\N就要服从他的判决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承您抬举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑道上是有障碍物没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就忍耐一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好，一次就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.99,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不服我的话\N就请你们退场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得下不为例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只红的看起来跑得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看它还在凶别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要选那只白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，它动也不动\N正在养精蓄锐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看只是在打瞌睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种类型\N在紧要关头才会使出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赌这只瞌睡虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照现在的赌盘来看\N你是没有赢的希望啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊，瞌睡虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不比比看怎么知道谁赢谁输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是开先锋艇的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那东西感觉怎么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是问你飞起来感觉怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.12,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上在一大片天空里\N好像只剩下我们自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是指你和那小子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为一个人没办法飞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔在天空感觉一定很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.89,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，这是今晚最后一场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.00,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精彩可期哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色火花今晚只要赢了\N就是五连霸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强势的红蛇\N应该也会有亮丽的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡王和绿色台风也不可忽视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，看仔细了下仔细了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要选红色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.58,0:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，不在工作岗位的时候\N就不要选红色的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色那只果然没什么人气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人气算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡虫，让大家对你刮目相看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.20,0:10:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格拉艾斯号的舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一副讨人厌的长相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色火花应该不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是金色好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，最后一场要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也快来呀，不要赶不上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？艾丽丝蒂亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你有没有看到拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面的往里面挤一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤口不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.81,0:11:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的关心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全看你的啰，红色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛全部的人都要赌同一只啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡虫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红色的快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超过它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好，不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是舰长\N看来又要刷新连胜记录了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡虫，你在干什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？莫蓝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色那只好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳赢的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是舰长，眼光真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.51,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想为\N像您这样的舰长效劳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位实在太幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪条船上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我过去曾在\N旗舰克劳索拉斯号上服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦德赛的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，他非常的了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.53,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也多亏了司令的栽培\N才能有今天的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我还有他的推荐信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他还活着啊\N那个乡下贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您看那个人的胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.51,0:13:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在战场出生入死的证明\N正是我的骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳纪斯会被度西斯占领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为\N麦德赛在作战中逃跑的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.02,0:13:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在那种胆小鬼的船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意当然是要多少有多少啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就是卑鄙小人的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种卑贱的东西\N你还真好意思拿出来给人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红色那只…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁才是卑鄙小人哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西对你很重要不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，要好好拿着才行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差一个\N我就可以出人头地了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.26,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝，你不管到哪里\N都可以混得很好的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色那只好厉害\N居然追上来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦，打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看连那只瞌睡虫\N都在努力奋战呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊，瞌睡虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.05,0:14:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊，冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下不削翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死也不能输呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.56,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，你的自尊到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.57,0:14:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太不够狠了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒！拿酒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡虫，只剩那只金色的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下可有看头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有惊无险哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.57,0:15:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里，舰长您选的金色\N怎么可能输给那些下等的鸟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是这么认为呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是作弊嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.63,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弱女子遭人欺负啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可以不去挺身搭救呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总不成眼睁睁在一旁看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.14,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.44,0:16:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在找尤莉丝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.11,0:16:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上听说\N有和EXILE相关的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会出现在最近的黑市拍卖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是图吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表面上这是一场\N奖金很高的先锋艇竞赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.39,0:16:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实背后同时也在进行着\N黑市交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚还挺热闹的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不是那些有钱的白痴贵族们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群凯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇你搞过头了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.52,0:16:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个大骗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.06,0:16:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.03,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在米纳纪斯连打都没打就逃的\N根本就只有你那艘格拉艾斯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.55,0:17:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一个小小的枪兵\N居然敢侮辱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这可是叛逆皇帝的重罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格拉艾斯号上\N全都是一群卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是不想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我渥克的船坞里\N不准有人随便乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.86,0:18:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这种像垃圾一样的枪兵侮辱\N教我怎么忍得下这口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侮辱人的应该是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.27,0:18:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你连一句道歉都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情大条了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要脏了您的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.79,0:18:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是用军舰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用军舰决斗\N看我把你连人带船一起击沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来当见证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体上船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就一起去跟阎王爷报到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那群野蛮的猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让他们知道我的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，那不会是银之战舰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说那家伙不就是\N亚力克斯．罗威了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是杀无赦的银之战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.01,0:19:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是无敌战舰…我们完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，有没有什么对策啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在开炮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.09,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果从背后攻击\N就算是银之战舰也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是还没有发信号耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要赢了\N事后理由大可以随便编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要发射吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮，射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好机会，射啊，射啊射啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要停给我射个痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，本舰大获全胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的银之战舰\N知道我的厉害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.03,0:20:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么那么慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要试试看那个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.94,0:20:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.97,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下可以跟令尊\N大大夸耀一番了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是\N父亲大人一定会很开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要确实作好记录的收集工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备发射多管喷射穿甲弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.65,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下你们完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.86,0:20:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无敌战舰的称号\N这下要让给我们格拉艾斯号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定信号弹已发出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.27,0:21:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞得那么夸张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发出信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定决斗结束，银之战舰获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.50,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会本着见证人的责任\N向国家进行报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.64,0:21:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追加…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也请替收拾善后的人想想好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是航行顺利结束\N再一起好好喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.11,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渥克 上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直太惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生还章给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好你没坐上那艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.23,0:22:40.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.14,0:22:58.21,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.28,0:23:03.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.89,0:23:12.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
